<h3> Welcome to Health 2.0 Advisors</h3><p>
Health 2.0 Advisors is the consulting and market intelligence arm of the Health 2.0 group of companies. Health 2.0 is changing how healthcare choices are made and how (and where) healthcare is delivered. We are here to help organizations of all sizes and industries to take advantage of Health 2.0-related innovations in ways that fit with the organization's objectives.</p><p>
How do we do that: Recognizing that different organizations have different needs, we create multiple ways for organizations to tap into our market intelligence and strategic advisory capabilities:</p>
<h4>Market Intelligence</h4><ul><li> 
<i>Database access. </i>We are developing the largest database of Health 2.0 companies, organizations, technologies, and news. We'll be making this available in 2010 to companies and individuals  
</li><li><i>Analytics.</i>We will be adding the ability for power users to do custom analysis of data early in 2011</li></ul></p>
<h4>Consulting services</h4><ul><li>
<i>Custom Consulting Projects-</i> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Examples include:<ul><li>
Growth strategies for Health 2.0 companies -  what opportunities to focus on first, which companies to partner with, etc.
</li><li>Portfolio strategies for companies wanting to take advantage of health 2.0 innovation to improve their performance, customer experience, etc.
</li><li>Strategies to respond to Health 2.0 changes to their business, e.g. how does mobile / unplatforms change our business model, what parts of our business are likely to be impacted now vs later, etc.
