</ul></li><li>
<i>Video-workshops-</i> short, intense sessions that address very sepcific or time-sensitive questions to help you move the needle immediatley</li>
<li><i>Cross-fires</i> 360 degrees feedback from experts on your new product launch plans, etc.</li>
<li><i>Executive Bootcamps-</i> when you have to make complex trade-offs under time-pressure or when different parts of the organization need to get on the same page</li></ul>
